name: Generative Flowers Viewer /(Collectors Gallery)
description:
This piece is a viewer for 'Bouquet of Flowers'. It fetches the list of all owners from objkt #404029 and displays the owners wallet specific version in realtime. Click/tap to view next owners flowers Press 's' to download image on desktop.
